  "prompt": "What is the best alarm clock?",
  "response": "The \"best\" alarm clock depends on your specific needs and preferences. Here are some popular types and recommendations:\n\n### 1. **Traditional Alarm Clocks**\n   - **Philips SmartSleep Wake-Up Light**: Simulates a sunrise to gently wake you up with light, also includes soothing sounds.\n   - **Sony ICFC-1T**: A classic, reliable analog alarm clock with a simple design and easy-to-use functions.\n\n### 2. **Smart Alarm Clocks**\n   - **Amazon Echo Spot**: Combines an alarm clock with Alexa voice control, allowing you to set alarms, check the weather, and more.\n   - **Lenovo Smart Clock with Google Assistant**: Compact and voice-controlled, integrates with other smart home devices.\n\n### 3. **Vibration Alarm Clocks**\n   - **Sonic Alert Sonic Boom**: Ideal for heavy sleepers or those with hearing impairments, it features a loud alarm and bed shaker.\n   - **Pillow Shaker Alarm Clock**: Vibration-based, great for those who need a silent but effective wake-up method.\n\n### 4. **Portable Alarm Clocks**\n   - **TravelWeely Portable Alarm Clock**: Small, lightweight, and battery-powered, perfect for travel.\n   - **JALL Wake-Up Light Alarm Clock**: Combines a portable design with a sunrise simulation feature.\n\n### 5. **Alarm Clocks for Kids**\n   - **LittleHippo Mella**: A colorful, interactive alarm clock that teaches kids when it\u2019s time to wake up or stay in bed.\n   - **OK to Wake! Alarm Clock & Night-Light**: Uses color changes to signal when it\u2019s okay for kids to get out of bed.\n\n### 6. **Alarm Clocks for Minimalists**\n   - **Loftie Clock**: A sleek, minimalist design with dual alarms and calming sleep sounds.\n   - **Norman Reversible Alarm Clock**: Simple, elegant, and reversible, with a clean design.\n\n### Features to Consider:\n- **Ease of Use**: Simple controls for setting and snoozing.\n- **Wake-Up Method**: Light, sound, vibration, or a combination.\n- **Smart Features**: Integration with voice assistants or smart home systems.\n- **Portability**: Compact and battery-powered for travelers.\n- **Customization**: Adjustable volume, light intensity, or alarm sounds.\n\nChoose the one that best fits your lifestyle and waking habits!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
